    "These results are shown graphically as success rates estimated by a mixed-effects model in Fig. 1.",
    "An aspect that cuts across the rough division into task types (reception, production, and translation) that I have not discussed here, but which calls for investigation, is accessibility to people with impairments, be it cognitive or physical (as well as children).",
    "This is an aspect that has recently received some attention (Arias-Badia and Torner, 2023, Rees, 2023), and the message so far is that digital dictionaries are not necessarily as accessible as we might wish.",
    "From that point of view, conversational chatbots are in principle able to adjust both the level of technicality (the now famous 'explain to me like I'm a tenyear-old'), and the modality of communication (e.g.",
    "via voice: speaking and listening)."
